title: Nightmare Before Christmas Wall Decals - Officially Licensed Disney Merchandise, 40 Unique Spooky Vinyl Stickers to Customise Your Walls, Easily Removable and Glow in The Dark | Paladone
features: HALLOWEEN DECORATIONS: Get ready for Halloween with these Nightmare Before Christmas wall decals. Featuring characters like Jack Skellington, Sally, and Zero, they add a fun and spooky touch to your home décor.

CUSTOMIZE YOUR WALLS: The pack includes four sheets totaling 40 different wall decals, providing ample options for a DIY redecoration. Enjoy the glow-in-the-dark feature from 16 of the decals for a spooky nighttime display.
EASY APPLICATIION AND REMOVAL: Perfect for decorating your walls, these decals are easy to apply and remove. Great for both kids and adults bedrooms or a themed room décor.
LICENSED DISNEY MERCH: These wall decals are officially licensed Disney merchandise, making them an ideal gift for any Tim Burton or Nightmare Before Christmas fan.

PALADONE MADE: This Jack Skellington product was designed responsibly in the UK by Paladone, the award-winning, global consumer products company. Paladone is a renowned creator of pop culture themed presents and novelty merchandise such as this decal set.
description: Give your room a spooky makeover with these Nightmare Before Christmas Wall Decals. The 40 vinyl stickers are removable, and 16 of them also glow in the dark! The four sheets include decals of Jack, Sally, Zero and more from the Tim Burton movie. Quick and easy to apply, you can transform your room into an amazing spectacle within just a few seconds. The Nightmare Before Christmas Wall Decals are perfect for decorating your home for Halloween as well as all year round.
